    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Highway Trust Fund Reform Act of 2015</b></p> <p> Repeals the Davis-Bacon Act (which requires that the locally prevailing wage rate be paid to laborers and mechanics working on federal-aid highway construction projects and public transportation construction projects).</p>]]></text>
